High Priestess Dyhna Zhyborrin was a follower of Jergal and the leader of the Crypt of Imminent Death in Bezantur in Thay during the midâ€“14 century DR.
Dyhna was the overseer of the temples staff. She also led worship services to Jergal and maintained a strong relationship with the clergy and followers of Kelemvor in Bezantur.
